      "content": "Your business was a huge part of your identity, and its failure has left a gaping hole in your life. It's understandable that you're struggling to face your family, but hiding from them won't make the guilt and shame go away. It may be worth considering reaching out to a therapist or support group where you can openly talk about your feelings and work through this difficult time. Be kind to yourself, and allow yourself the time and space to grieve the loss of your business.",
