      "content": "but that's the thing... they'll have to deal with the mess i've made regardless. every day i stay, i'm just digging the hole deeper. the debt, the legal stuff, the constant stress I'm putting on them... it's like a toxin. if i'm gone, at least the momentum of the disaster stops. i'm just a walking reminder of everything that went wrong. wouldn't it be more merciful to just cut the cord before it gets even worse?",
